headline.main: U.S. Strike in Yemen Kills Former Guantanamo Bay Detainee
headline.print_headline: U.S. Strike in Yemen Kills Former Guantanamo Bay Detainee

lead_paragraph: The Pentagon said on Monday that a March 2 strike against al Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula in Yemen killed a former detainee from the U.S. detention center at Guantanamo Bay, Cuba.
